  575: each funds a **greedy** set under a budget of one-third of total project cost, is
  576: eligible to fund a project only where *its own* noisy estimate of net is positive
  577: (no oracle gate), and its delivered value is scored on the projects' *true* net.
  578: The arms are symmetric except for the coverage mechanism and its matched
  579: counterparts. *Distributed (endogenous coverage):* each interested citizen reports
  580: independently with probability p if her value v ≥ 0 and p·(1 − β) if v < 0 (adverse
  581: voice bias), giving ĥS_D = Σreports / p, ranked by estimated net per cost.
  582: *Central (competent value-reader):* an appraisal budget matched to the distributed
