  156: advantage is **real but small — pre-registered pooled median ≈0.025 of the full-information benchmark, below
  157: the pre-registered 0.05 research-program rebuild gate** (not a policy-materiality threshold; 18/18 cells
  158: positive; post-hoc ratio-of-sums 0.026 [0.023, 0.029]; rises with credit pressure, falls as credit aligns with
  159: value). Therefore: **Path B — publish the architecture + qualitative mechanism; retire the calibrated
